<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bent-adj">bent <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bent/    美 /bent/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>弯曲的；驼背的；弯腰的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a bent nail
弯曲的指甲</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a bent old man
驼背老人</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-bent-on-doing-sth">(be) bent on (doing) sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>下决心做某事</strong>  </p></div>